<inglise> 96/463/EC: Council Decision of 23 July 1996 designating the reference body responsible for collaborating in rendering uniform the testing methods and the assessment of the results for pure-bred breeding animals of the bovine species </inglise>
<eesti> N&Otilde;UKOGU OTSUS 96/463/E&Uuml;, millega m&auml;&auml;ratakse asutus, mis vastutab koost&ouml;&ouml; eest t&otilde;upuhaste aretusveiste kontrollimeetodite ja tulemuste hindamise &uuml;htlustamise eest 23. juuli 1996 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COUNCIL OF THE EUROPEAN UNION, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE N&Otilde;UKOGU, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa &Uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the proposal from the Commission, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse komisjoni ettepanekut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Directive 87/328/EEC of 18 June 1987 on the acceptance for breeding purposes of pure-bred breeding animals of the bovine species (1), and in particular Article 5 thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 18. juuni 1987. aasta direktiivi 87/328/EM&Uuml; t&otilde;upuhaste aretusveiste t&otilde;uaretuses vastuv&otilde;etavaks tunnistamise kohta, (1) eriti selle artiklit 5, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in order to render uniform the testing methods and the assessment of the results when pure-bred breeding animals of the bovine species are accepted for breeding purposes, a reference body should be designated; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: tuleks m&auml;&auml;rata asutus t&otilde;upuhaste aretusveiste t&otilde;uaretuses vastuv&otilde;etavaks tunnistamisel kasutatavate kontrollimeetodite ja saadud tulemuste hindamise &uuml;htlustamiseks; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the powers and duties of that body should be defined; </inglise>
<eesti> tuleks m&auml;&auml;ratleda k&otilde;nealuse asutuse volitused ja kohustused; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, in the light of experience gained, the Interbull Centre should be designated as the reference body responsible for collaborating in rendering uniform the testing methods and the assessment of the results for pure-bred breeding animals of the bovine species, </inglise>
<eesti> saadud kogemusi silmas pidades tuleks t&otilde;upuhaste aretusveiste kontrollimeetodite ja tulemuste hindamise &uuml;htlustamisel tehtava koost&ouml;&ouml; eest vastutavaks asutuseks m&auml;&auml;rata Interbull Centre, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS DECISION: </inglise>
